dct_title_s: Map of Cape May County, New Jersey showing inland water ways from Cape May to Bay Head
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Cape May Point to Atlantic City along the Atlantic Coast. Map advertises for a channel that is to become popular for yachting and motor boating. Waterway is shown in red and property being developed by the South Jersey Realty Co. is also shown.
